name: devil's party

_

Beloved devil,
I beg that you will reinsert me in the darkness, 
set me free of all this fake bullshit 
and bless me with your sinful exit. 

Give me such confidence to go fuck everyone else, 
that even when I'm down, 
I will tear them apart as well. 
Give me sex, money and lust, 
because I put all my darkness into yourself, 
my saviour Lucifer.
